{
  "projectId": "{{project_id}}",
  "imageInfos": [
    {
      "imagePath": "{{image_path}}",
      "mimeType": "JPEG"
    }
  ],
  "prompt": "Generate a compelling variation of this character in a completely different scene. Show Aelindra Vaelstrom in a quiet, intimate moment of deep arcane ritual inside an impossibly vast ancient elven library. She kneels at the centre of a circular stone dais three metres in diameter, its surface inscribed with dense glowing runic script in violet and silver light. Her right hand is pressed flat against the dais as a web of arcane violet energy radiates outward from her palm across the entire floor in fractal geometric patterns. Her left hand holds her crescent-moon staff upright beside her. Her silver hair falls loosely downward as she leans forward in intense concentration. She is wearing the same midnight-blue constellation cloak and violet-gold inner robes. The library surrounding her stretches impossibly tall — carved obsidian bookshelves ascending hundreds of metres to vaulted gothic cathedral ceilings, every shelf packed with ancient leather-bound tomes. Thousands of spellbooks float open in mid-air throughout the space, their pages turning slowly on their own, emitting soft violet and blue ambient light. Countless glowing arcane dust motes and tiny sparks drift through the air. The overall lighting is a deep, mystical blue-violet from the tomes and runes with no direct light source — pure ambient magical glow. Mood: contemplative, mysterious, ancient, and awe-inspiring."
}

